source.name: Planning Neighborhoods
source.description:
Neighborhoods according to the Department of City Planning.
Data are available in zipped ESRI shapefile format. These boundaries are designed soley for the Planning Department's neighborhood notifications.
A map showing the boundaries of these neighborhoods can be found here: http://sf-planning.org/index.aspx?page=1654

An Excel spreadsheet of Neighborhood Groups contact details can be found here: http://www.sf-planning.org/ftp/files/publications_reports/Neighborhood_Mailing_List.xls.

There are alternative neighborhood boundaries (which include a larger number of neighborhoods) here: https://data.sfgov.org/d/ejmn-jyk6
